Finally, we can also investigate the Re´nyi index dependence for non-integer values of q. In Fig. 7 we

report numerical linked expansions results for (a) O(2) [152] and (b) O(3) [151] together with different es-

timates for the Ising ﬁxed point, as well as our estimate for free scalar [163]. The non-trivial q-dependences

are qualitatively similar, and the ratio between O(2) and O(1) is well compatible with 2, as well as for O(3)

with a factor 3.

