b. Interacting systems: Luttinger liquids— For one-dimensional critical (zero-temperature) Luttinger liquids, taking a subsystem of length , its RDM can be described as the thermal density matrix of an open Luttinger liquid with the same velocity u and Luttinger parameter K [271, 276] at an effective low

